if I tell you everything.

619
00:40:44,650 --> 00:40:46,950
Does it mean you won't tell me
for my own good?

620
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:49,680
You are really an old jerk.

621
00:40:50,570 --> 00:40:51,950
What do you know?

622
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:55,990
Let's go.

623
00:40:59,610 --> 00:41:01,280
Many things happened back then

624
00:41:01,570 --> 00:41:03,200
but I have no time to tell you now.

625
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:05,089
Feng has Zhang Nian leading him.

626
00:41:05,090 --> 00:41:06,680
He acts in an unorthodox way.

627
00:41:06,730 --> 00:41:07,870
I'll tell you everything

628
00:41:08,020 --> 00:41:09,160
